    • Method Detail

      • accept

        public boolean accept(String className,
                      URL classUrl,
                      URL classPathUrl)
        Invoked to determine if class can be accepted. default behavior returns true.
        Parameters:
        className - Name of the class.
        classUrl - URL for the class resource.
        classPathUrl - URL for the class path resource that contains the class resource. If the URL protocol is file, it would be the path to root package. If the URL protocol is jar, it would be the jar file.
        Returns:
        true to accept the given class, false otherwise.
